title: #92Noon! Anthony Barr was gone, then he wasn't?
description: Heavy on Free Agency talkers with Florio joining in the first hour! Tom Chorske calls in to chat hockey and his two children winning state titles, Jordan Leopold is in studio in support of a tremendous cause...and then we find out Anthony Barr will NOT be joining the Jets. Fun show.
